            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td>$149/mo</td><td class="cell-yes">$99/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Articles written for you</td><td class="cell-no">No — research tool only</td><td class="cell-yes">30 / month</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Auto-publishes to your CMS</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">WordPress · Webflow · Ghost</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Google Business Profile posts</td><td class="cell-no">Not included</td><td class="cell-yes">30 GBP posts / month</td></tr>
