        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">The execution math</div>
          <p>Every SEO.AI subscriber we interviewed underestimated this by roughly <strong>20x</strong>. They saw $149/mo and budgeted $149/mo. They actually spend $2,668+/mo to turn that data into published pages. The tool is honest about what it does — the gap is in how customers calculate their <em>real</em> SEO budget.</p>
