        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — how SEO.AI stacks up</h2>
        <p>SEO.AI's content quality is rated as <strong>publish-ready for businesses currently producing zero content</strong>. Users who want pull quotes, custom bullet styles, and visual variety report needing light editing. Brand Voice calibration is the single most-praised feature in customer interviews — it genuinely raises the floor versus generic AI writers.</p>

        <h3>CMS coverage by competing AI SEO platforms</h3>

        <div class="chart-card">
          <div class="chart-head">
            <div>
              <div class="chart-title">CMS coverage by competing AI SEO platforms (2026)</div>
              <div class="chart-sub">Native integrations · custom webhook excluded</div>
